$s well as there; and perhaps may be &s;omewhere
$$e and not there.</P>
<P>And that I may with the mo&s;t Impartial Care
$$ther Repre&s;ent the Inju&s;tice of this placing our
$$pieties at the Period afore&s;aid, it is humbly
<HI>$ffered,</HI> That the true <HI>Source</HI> of all this <HI>Deluge of
$$piety,</HI> is rather to be plac'd at that Wretched
$word$ Unhappy Time, when Iniquity was E&s;tab|$$ed
