Son of the afore&s;aid King <HI>Ja&mdash;s</HI> renew'd the &s;ame
<PB N="10" REF="9">
War again&s;t Heaven, which his Father had
wickedly begun, by Reprinting the &s;aid Procla|mation,
and adding his own Authority to renew
