Character of a <HI>Puritan.</HI></P>
<P><PB N="15" REF="14">
<HI>The Church,</HI> formerly the pure Temple of Di|$$ine
Adoration, and the Place where True Re|ligion
was <HI>Taught;</HI> the Go&s;pel of our Lord Je&s;us
<HI>Propagated,</HI> Youth <HI>Catechi&s;ed</HI> and <HI>In&s;tructed,</HI> and
God <HI>Honoured;</HI> now became the Theatre of
