God <HI>with them.</HI> No &s;ooner was the Ser|vice
Ended, but the Bells began to Ring, the
Ale-Hou&s;e open, the People, fall to Dancing, and
Revelling&mdash;<HI>the ble&s;&s;ed Equivolent to Queen</HI>
Elizabeth's <HI>Reformation.</HI></P>
<P>The Sober Religious, Godly Family's who
with their old Mini&s;ters, abhored this way of
