<P>Come we next to Enquire Concerning the Pe|riod
where the&s;e Gentlemen have placed it
(<HI>Viz.</HI>) The late Rebellion; from which it ma
<PB N="17" REF="16">
be allowed it had an Addition; tho' I cannot al|low
