<P>But then it would be Natural to Enquire from
which Party, or from which Side, either of
King or Parliament, during that Unnatural Re|bellion,
the <HI>Deluge of Impiety</HI> afore&s;aid, receiv'd
the greate&s;t Addition: And tho' the mighty
