<P>But they that know the Strength of
the <HI>Prote&s;tant Doctrine,</HI> the Orthodox
Foundation of the Church of <HI>England
Principles,</HI> and the Ability of her D I|VINES
to <HI>Defend it,</HI> Contemn the
