<P>For this Rea&s;on, they have on all
Occa&s;ions, powerfully Re&s;i&s;ted, and
Succe&s;sfully al&s;o, all the Errors of the
Times, to this Day; and have now &s;et
about that mo&s;t Effectual Step to fix a
good Foundation of RELIGION
in Po&s;terity, as the be&s;t Means to fix
